Package io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.models

Class IP

java.lang.Object
io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.models.IP
public class IP extends Object
An IP consists of an id, an ip, an ip version, if it is a subnet, the reverse lookup information, a type and if it is floating.
